        "mainbody": "'''Charri Hunzrin''' was a [[drow]] of [[Menzoberranzan]] and the heir of [[House Hunzrin]] in the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].",
        "History": "In the {{YearlinkName|1486}}, Charri discussed with her mother, Matron Mother [[Shakti Hunzrin]], about forging an alliance with [[House Melarn]] in order to attack the reformed [[House Do'Urden]].\n\nSome months later, Charri went alongside the young [[Shak'kral Hunzrin]] to a meeting with a clan of [[spriggan]] followers of [[Malcanthet]] in [[Damara]] arranged by the Hunzrin trader [[Denderida]]."
